name: AI Eight Puzzle & Tower of Hanoi Examples built on Common Lisp and Clojure
tagline: AI project examples built on common lisp and clojure
body:
aiproj ====== AI project examples built on common lisp and clojure Running eight-puzzle ----------

Common Lisp version

* eightpuzzle.execer : Mac intel 64 binary * eightpuzzle.fas : ansi common lisp fas `compile-file` output (runs where clisp exists) * deliver.lisp : for compiling and running with lispworks

Clojure version

In directory of `eight-puzzle` : `lein run` Running hanoi ----------

Clojure version

In directory of `hanoi-test` : `lein run n` where `n` goes for pegs
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
